<task id="to_roam_a_network_license_on_a_client_computer">
   <title>Roaming a network license on a client computer</title>
   <shortdesc />
   <taskbody>
      <context id="context_w1t_rvc_cnb">A network license can be roamed to use <b conkeyref="product_names_warehouse/b_lhg_1q1_cnb" /> without connection to the license
         server (work outside of the office, at home, ...).<p>When a network license is used on a
            client computer, the <uicontrol>Roaming...</uicontrol> button is displayed in the <xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006706253-LicenseManager" format="html" scope="external">Licensing Information</xref><!-- (needs link)-->
            dialog box.</p><fig id="fig_ws2_qph_smb">
            <image href="https://storage.googleapis.com/bricsys-help-en/help/en_US/V20/BCAD/InstallationAndSettings/LicensingInformation_Roaming.png" id="image_vzf_qph_smb" scope="external" />
         </fig></context>
      <steps id="ol_xv3_pph_smb">
         <step>
            <cmd>If your computer is connected to the license server through a proxy server, click the <xref keyref="GD_proxy_settings">Proxy Settings</xref> button to configure the proxy settings for a network license.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step>
            <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Roaming...</uicontrol> button.</cmd>
            <stepresult>The <uicontrol>Roaming</uicontrol> dialog box opens.<fig id="fig_m4g_rph_smb">
                  <image href="https://storage.googleapis.com/bricsys-help-en/help/en_US/V20/BCAD/InstallationAndSettings/Roaming_Checkout.png" id="image_msh_rph_smb" scope="external" />
               </fig></stepresult>
         </step>
         <step>
            <cmd>Enter the number of days you want to check out the license for roaming and click the <uicontrol>Checkout</uicontrol> button.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step>
            <cmd>(Optional) Tick the checkbox if you want to automatically refresh the roaming period when your computer is connected to the server.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step>
            <cmd>Restart <b conkeyref="product_names_warehouse/b_lhg_1q1_cnb" /> to apply the
               changes.</cmd>
         </step>
      </steps>
   </taskbody>
